                        Which MBA specialization has the best career prospects?
                        <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>The "best" specialization depends on your interests, strengths, and industry trends. Finance and consulting typically offer the highest starting salaries. Marketing provides diverse opportunities across industries. Operations is valuable in manufacturing and supply chain-focused companies. Technology management and analytics are rapidly growing fields with excellent prospects. The ideal approach is to choose a specialization that aligns with both your strengths and market demand.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
