                        <p>The ROI varies significantly by institution tier. Top-tier schools (IIMs, ISB) offer excellent ROI despite higher fees, with average salaries of ₹20-28 LPA and strong career progression. Mid-tier schools provide good ROI with moderate fees and salaries of ₹10-18 LPA. Lower-tier schools may offer questionable ROI unless they have specific industry connections or regional strengths. Consider not just starting salary but long-term career trajectory, network value, and personal growth when evaluating ROI.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
